<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=DNA_repair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small" style="column-count:2;-moz-column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
